name: test Get Calculated Historical Providers for Client 1
fullName: /SchedulingOptimizationRegression//Historical Data in Clinic Algorithm//C951299 Preferred client gets scheduled with their most preferred provider#test Get Calculated Historical Providers for Client 1
descriptionHtml:
### [https://centralreach.atlassian.net/browse/CRCH-18161](https://centralreach.atlassian.net/browse/CRCH-18161)
Request Description

This endpoint sends an HTTP GET request to retrieve refreshed historical preferred providers for a specific client's scheduling settings.

### Request Body

This request does not require a request body.

### Response

The response for this request is in the form of a JSON object with the following schema:

``` json
{
"type": "object",
"properties": {
"preferredProviders": {
"type": "array",
"items": {}
},
"result": {
"type": "string"
},
"failed": {
"type": "boolean"
},
"cachedTime": {
"type": "integer"
}
}
}

```

The response includes the following key-value pairs:

- `preferredProviders`: An array of preferred providers

- `result`: A string indicating the result of the operation

- `failed`: A boolean value indicating if the operation failed

- `cachedTime`: An integer representing the cached time
